reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 25, 2022
reviews.reviewText: The phone screen is unique and I really live the color. It’s VERY EASY TO PUT ON. The color of the screen however does naturally make is difficult to see the screen in certain types of light. A small price to pay in my opinion, and it’s far and few between. It does crack EASILY. I had mine about two weeks before I got my first crack, which quickly spread from its original location to completely across the screen, but it’s remains on phone, doesn’t impede my usage and continued to protect my privacy. Another thing I must mention is the privacy factor is high… which makes it difficult when you want to share watching your screen with a friend. The angle has to be just Perfect if you BOTH want to see it, it requires a lot of readjusting your position but it’s doable.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 17, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars exactly what I was looking for
reviews.reviewText: after breaking the last privacy protector that I had, I was interested in finding something with a little more “pop” to it when I found this. can definitely say this hit the mark because every time I am at a meeting or out somewhere I get so many questions about my phoneobviously if someone is standing directly behind you they will still be able to see the screen but as far as being able to be out in public and not worry about someone looking over and seeing something they shouldn’t (or preventing people from taking pictures of my phone)? you will be more than pleased with how this privacy protector does. I will give the warning that if you are wearing polarized sunglasses the screen will be near impossible to see, something to think aboutwill definitely be buying this product again, installation was a breeze thanks to the guide provided. it does tend to catch a lot of fingerprints because of the reflective screen but super easy to wipe away and make look new. the only reason that I knocked one star off this review is because it did seem to chip/crack fairly easily (needing to get a new one as I type this) but that is part of the deal with glass screen protectors. rather that than your screen

reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars It’s not super pivate
reviews.reviewText: I love the color of the screen and it’s a REALLY good screen protector it’s nice and thick but just the right amount of thick. reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Pretty, works, cracks easily
reviews.reviewText: I really like this case. It’s the best for privacy since it’s mirror-like to anyone at an angle. The color of the reflection is a pink/reddish color. I’ve received a lot of compliments on it. The only thing is, is that it cracks easily. I drop my phone a lot, so Ive had to repurchase this 3 times in a short period. :/ Also, it sometimes makes my phone glitch with not being able to touch the screen when I’m on a phone call. It’s weird. It only happens when this screen is on.
